---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[95%] xl:max-w-7xl bg-white rounded-[2rem] border border-orange-100 shadow-2xl shadow-orange-950/5 overflow-hidden grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 relative z-10 mt-6 min-h-[85vh] animate-entrance">

    <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-slate-950 text-white p-8 sm:p-16 relative flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-orange-600/20 via-slate-900 to-slate-950"></div>

        <div class="floating-badge top-16 -right-4 sm:right-10 z-30 animate-float-1 text-base">
            <span class="text-2xl">🎁</span> Primera clase GRATIS
        </div>
        <div class="floating-badge bottom-20 left-4 sm:left-10 z-30 animate-float-2 delay-200 text-base">
            <span class="text-emerald-500 text-xl">●</span> Plazas limitadas
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 w-full overflow-hidden mt-8">
            <div class="flex w-[300%] animate-slider hover:[animation-play-state:paused]">
                <div class="w-1/3 flex-shrink-0 px-4">
                    <span class="text-orange-400 text-sm font-black tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Módulo 01</span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight">Desarrollo Web Frontend</h2>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-slate-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-md">Maqueta webs estáticas a la velocidad de la luz. Aprende HTML, CSS moderno y Javascript puro desde cero.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/3 flex-shrink-0 px-4">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 text-sm font-black tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Módulo 02</span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight">Bases de Datos & Backend</h2>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-slate-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-md">Crea tu propia API, conecta con bases de datos SQL y gestiona usuarios. El cerebro de cualquier app.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/3 flex-shrink-0 px-4">
                    <span class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-black tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Módulo 03</span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight">Despliegue & Servidores</h2>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-slate-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-md">Sube tus proyectos a internet con Vercel o un VPS propio. Que el mundo vea tu trabajo online.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono tracking-widest uppercase bg-slate-900 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-slate-800">Deslizando Automáticamente</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-5 p-8 sm:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center gap-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-50/40 to-transparent">
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-orange-100 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-orange-800 uppercase tracking-wide border border-orange-200/50">
                👨‍💻 Clases Particulares
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 leading-[1.05]">
                APRENDE A <br />
                <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-amber-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                    PROGRAMAR
                </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 font-medium">
                Clases personalizadas, prácticas desde el día uno y adaptadas a tu ritmo para convertirte en un desarrollador preparado para el mundo laboral.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-orange-200/50 mt-4">
            <a href="mailto:tuemail@ejemplo.com" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-amber-500 py-5 text-base font-black text-white tracking-wider uppercase shadow-xl shadow-orange-500/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:brightness-105 hover:-translate-y-1">
                ✉️ Enviar Correo Personal
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>